      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable transportation option for those on a budget. While the engine and transmission are functional, the car shows clear signs of its age, including some fading on the exterior paint and noticeable wear on the interior seating. There are no major mechanical failures, but a few minor repairs and standard maintenance will likely be needed in the near future. It is a dependable driver that offers great value for a buyer willing to put in a little bit of work to refresh its appearance.",
