    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me every single day. It runs great and still looks sharp on the road\u2014perfect if you're looking for a dependable car that's been well-loved! I've taken good care of it, and I'm sure you're going to love it as much as I have. Feel free to shoot me a message if you want to come by and take it for a spin!",
      "price": 29500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 2008 Porsche Cayman S features the mid-mounted 3.4L M97 flat-six engine, delivering exceptional balance and a 7,200 RPM redline. Equipped with a crisp 6-speed manual transaxle, the drivetrain remains tight with precise gear engagement. The chassis benefits from a McPherson strut arrangement and staggered alloys, providing neutral handling and high lateral grip. Recent service includes a full cooling system flush and inspection of the VarioCam Plus timing. The braking system utilizes four-piston monobloc calipers for consistent deceleration and firm pedal feel. While showing honest signs of use consistent with its age, the mechanical integrity is robust, offering a pure analog driving experience for the discerning enthusiast.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
