    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle strikes the perfect balance between luxury and everyday utility. The exterior features a deep metallic finish that retains a brilliant luster, complemented by well-preserved alloy wheels. While there are a few minor stone chips on the front hood and a small scuff on the rear bumper consistent with careful use, the body remains straight and free of any major blemishes. Inside, the cabin is a testament to pride of ownership; the premium leather upholstery is supple and clean, with only slight creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster. All electronic components, including the touchscreen navigation, heated seats, and dual-zone climate control, are in perfect working order. Mechanically, the car is robust. It comes with a comprehensive service history, including a recent oil change and a full brake service performed last month. The engine runs quietly, the transmission shifts smoothly, and the tires have significant tread remaining. This is a reliable, high-quality car that is ready for the road today.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
