      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting a refined example of automotive engineering, this vehicle represents a premier opportunity for the discerning driver. Meticulously maintained and displaying consistent mechanical excellence, the car offers a balanced profile of performance and reliability. Its aesthetic condition remains impressive, reflecting a history of attentive care and responsible ownership. This offering delivers exceptional value for those seeking a sophisticated driving experience and proven durability.",
