      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in really nice shape and has plenty of life left in it\u2014perfect for someone looking for a solid, reliable set of wheels without the brand-new price tag. It runs smoothly and has been well-loved during my time with it. I'd love for it to go to a good home where it'll be appreciated! Feel free to reach out if you want to take it for a spin!",
