    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically robust 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six power plant. This example is equipped with the desirable 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a factory-spec variable M differential lock. Critical preventive maintenance has been addressed, including a comprehensive double-VANOS service and rear subframe reinforcement to ensure structural integrity under high lateral loads. The induction system utilizes its original individual throttle bodies for instantaneous throttle response. While the exterior shows minor road-wear consistent with its 'good' designation, the powertrain remains tight with no rod bearing noise and linear power delivery to the 8,000 RPM redline. A true enthusiast's chassis ready for spirited driving.",
